   5:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * ============================================================
   6:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *
   7:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * Decode functions for all confirmed GCU attrs.
   8:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * Promoted from private statics in movi_comm.c to public
   9:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * functions so they can be called directly on captured
  10:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * byte arrays for testing without a live gimbal.
  11:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *
  12:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * Each function is self-contained:
  13:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   - checks attr ID and minimum length before touching dst
  14:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   - sets the corresponding valid flag on success
  15:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   - does not touch any other fields in dst
  16:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *
  17:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * hamfly_pump() calls all of these automatically.
  18:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * Direct use is for testing or custom polling.
  19:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  */
