  27:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * Big-endian read helpers
  28:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * Attr 1, 4, 287 payloads are big-endian, no sub-index byte.
  29:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * Attr 22 is little-endian with a 0x00 sub-index at offset 0.
