 147:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c **** /* ============================================================
 148:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * hamfly_decode_attitude  --  attr 22
 149:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *
 150:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * plen=19, all LE int16, sub-index byte at off 0 (ignored).
 151:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * Note: Java field label "Roll" at off 1 is actually Pitch
 152:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * in observed data. Layout confirmed against live GCU.
 153:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   off  1-2  LE int16: Pitch  /100  deg
 154:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   off  3-4  LE int16: Yaw    /100  deg
 155:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   off  5-6  LE int16: Roll   /100  deg
 156:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   off  7-8  LE int16: Roll error   /10 deg
 157:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   off  9-10 LE int16: Pitch error  /10 deg
 158:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   off 11-12 LE int16: Yaw error    /10 deg
 159:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   off 13-14 LE int16: Roll rate    /10 dps
 160:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   off 15-16 LE int16: Pitch rate   /10 dps
 161:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  *   off 17-18 LE int16: Yaw rate     /10 dps
 162:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_telemetry.c ****  * ============================================================ */
